for linux mint


1) curl -fsSL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_14.x | sudo -E bash -

2) sudo apt-get install -y nodejs

3) to verify install->    node --version
    to verify install->    npm --version



node application

4) npm init

5) npm install uuid

6) npm install -D nodemon

//for a webhost installation -> npm install 
//will create all modules automatically
